rows.label: tev036001_MSG0001
rows.name:
Have you ever noticed how how cheerful Ma-non are?
They don't seem to have a problem being stuck on this
middle-of-nowhere planet, do they?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036001_MSG0002
rows.name:
But I think we're kidding ourselves, don't you? I mean,
we may never be able to return to to our homeworld
again, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036001_MSG0003
rows.name:
Anyway, the longer I stay on the ship, the sadder I get.
So I make a point to come down here and talk to to
Fraisie every day, if that makes sense?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036001_MSG0004
rows.name:
The things she says, they... Well, I guess they just fill
some hole in my heart? I wish I could share this feeling
with with with everyone![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036001_MSG0011
rows.name:
There's a water-purification plant right there, but it's
not enough to pump out the amount of water a city
this size needs, is it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036001_MSG0012
rows.name:
Still, did you know that there's a lake west of New LA
filled with fresh, clean water?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036001_MSG0013
rows.name:
If we could pipe that water into the city somehow,
I bet we could take care of our hydration worries,
right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036001_MSG0016
rows.name:
Anyway, the human working over at the purification
plant was on board with the idea, mostly?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036001_MSG0017
rows.name:
I hope they're able to to get started on construction
without any setbacks, don't you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036001_MSG0034
rows.name:
Did you hear that they finished up the new waterworks
on Biahno Lake?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036001_MSG0035
rows.name:
I hear the Ma-non on the ship are also happy,
you know? Mostly because their relief supplies now
include a steady supply of of water.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036001_MSG0036
rows.name: We need water to live just as much as you do, right?[ST:wait ]
